  _lines:
  - I don't think so.
  - I believe it is in the mere interest of every living being.
  - To give as much back to the community as they can...
  - Before it's too late.
  - But that's enough of that.
  - I don't like to waste people's time.
  - Especially of someone as youtful as yourself.
  - Just get me something to remember the times with.
